mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一種劇毒感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n期待 關公 有帽衛衣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9065e35222ad4c16bbd651e00e37809766fb578d","tid":476943,"uid":29551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T05:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痴撚線，人地私下whatsapp你唔公開講就係想俾面你，係都要on99自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n毓民都已經廢時係節目屌佢地,班垃圾又想激到毓民屌佢地幫毓民谷收視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毓民係節目屌親佢地閒閒地都幾萬人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n圖都無堅定流都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2c8f4e4cd65eecace3a38e9c04f7ce1aada5b2","tid":476943,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"鳩達幫毓民報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c341bd4b413a6b7bdb9aafd10bcc8a8e821b4a","tid":476943,"uid":137569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"熱狗無㗎啦，年宵都要㨂去旺角搞，如果仲可以捱到書展都真係靠神跡"},{"pid":"1818846401199a41d394ffbf791287fee528e1a3","tid":476943,"uid":135217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗無㗎啦，年宵都要㨂去旺角搞，如果仲可以捱到書展都真係靠神跡</blockquote><br />\n佢係咁縮成本應該有排捱<br />\n等緊一個民綷機會大反擊<br />\n<br />\n到時又有新血唔知頭唔知路課金<br />\n多咗觀眾又會多廣告收入<br />\n跟住又有錢攪散本土<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64676af42e0c8e9471818757c41263fa48a8129","tid":476943,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T14:55:33.000Z","msg":"將私人whatsapp公諸如世嚟公審；似足當年老毛公開彭德懷份萬言書嚟上綱上線開展鬥爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021574227fbd233c1fc9ff118d92eaba6dc9c80f","tid":476943,"uid":135217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:40:20.000Z","msg":"蝗上話毓民辱罵佢老婆做「賊婆」<br />\n但係佢自己都侮辱過唔少人啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb1277d990bd17611dd18474e8edb1ebc37d386","tid":476943,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/234415_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F234415_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=77d1ff13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19a87cba4e63af00c7fb821b34cc5b17c23fb9a2","tid":476943,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"講開又講，以前黃洋達出走人力都係「反轉豬肚就係屎」，一反面就屌到舊東主仆街<br />\n依家同黃毓民反面就懶係義正辭嚴，「小弟」前「先生」後，一副受害者模樣搏同情，真係兩面三刀嘅典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果覺得道理真係喺自己果邊嘅咪屌返毓民轉頭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e3b326339fec3456c5422a22bae6f81d13493f","tid":476943,"uid":4389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/234415_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F234415_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=77d1ff13&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黃洋達根本想小事化大，私下WhatsApp 通知你俾單據計清欠款算俾足面子。<br />\n<br />\n其次再收到恐嚇信叫你收手，唔好再玩小學雞伎倆，點知你公諸於世，連下台階都唔要。<br />\n<br />\n而家你只有鞏固到熱狗圍爐死忠，熱血時報無新水魚搵笨，離倒閉日子不遠。"},{"pid":"9696da52414021752835a97a1466dc9f6de7c958","tid":476943,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T17:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/23/234415_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F23%2F234415_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=77d1ff13&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黃洋達根本想小事化大，私下WhatsApp 通知你俾單據計清欠款算俾足面子。<br />\n<br />\n其次再收到恐嚇信叫你收手，唔好再玩小學雞伎倆，點知你公諸於世，連下台階都唔要。<br />\n<br />\n而家你只有鞏固到熱狗圍爐死忠，熱血時報無新水魚搵笨，離倒閉日子不遠。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鳩達死唔斷氣<br />\n我諗熱狗情況比大家想像差<br />\n由萬人圍屌<br />\n到書展蝕到空虛<br />\n到不斷開項目cap水<br />\n到冇外人理既圍爐台慶"},{"pid":"4cc2c481c926dba3f0e457875f15bd000ff5454b","tid":476943,"uid":54223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"拿，我而家話你聽呀，<br />\n<br />\n黃洋達你呢個賤人呢，一定係仆街之中既仆街！"}]}